I89. Regulations

I11The Administrator may establish regulations for the administration of this chapter.

I53(Added Pub. L. 105ÿ09304, title V, ÿ1A502, Oct. 28, 1998, 112 Stat. 2912.)

I80ÿ1A1318

I89. Copies of records

I11Upon payment of the prescribed fee, any person may obtain a certified copy of any official record of the Office of the Administrator that relates to this chapter. That copy shall be admissible in evidence with the same effect as the original.

I53(Added Pub. L. 105ÿ09304, title V, ÿ1A502, Oct. 28, 1998, 112 Stat. 2913.)

